# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Scrape/research caches never enter this repo
.firecrawl/

# Populated compliance reference caches never enter this repo.
# They are YOUR organization's live compliance posture (failing tests, open
# vulnerabilities, document gaps). Only the committed *.template.md files and
# vanta-config.json ship; /vanta-sync writes the real vanta-*.md next to them
# (or to $VANTA_REFERENCES_DIR), and those stay local.
references/*.md
!references/*.template.md
